Rockchip Yocto BSP
===============================

Supported boards
----------------

In order to know the supported boards, please, see the release notes at

   http://rockchip.wikidot.com/yocto-user-guide#toc1

Quick Start Guide
-----------------

Once you have downloaded the source of all projects, you will have to
call:

$: machine=<MACHINE> . ./setup-environment -t <x11/wayland> -b <build_dir>

After this step, you will be with everything need for build an image.

To get more info, see at

   http://rockchip.wikidot.com/yocto-user-guide
